# KEEP THESE (Code & Structure)
# ============================================
# All .cs files are included
# All .prefab files are included
# All .unity scene files are included
# All .asset ScriptableObject files are included
# All .meta files are included (Unity needs them)
# ProjectSettings/ is included
# Packages/ manifest is included
